\/27\/surah-al-fatihah-greatest\/","url_meta":{"origin":3604,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Al-Fatihah greatest chapter of the Book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id ibn al-Mu\u2019alla reported: I was praying in the mosque when the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, called out to me but I did not respond. I said later, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I was praying.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDid not Allah say: Respond to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3607,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/11\/lord-delight-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":3604,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Allah delights in one who prays, fears Him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYour Lord delights in a shepherd who announces the call to prayer on the peak of a mountain and he prays. Allah Almighty says: Behold My servant who calls to prayer, performs prayer, and fears\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36849,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/29\/allah-marvels-abd\/","url_meta":{"origin":3604,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Istighfar: Allah marvels at believer seeking forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina El